{"tid":1250211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽人講，香口膠跡難以清理","createTime":"2019-06-22T03:55:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T04:34:39.000Z","uid":260806,"like":3,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4bf57be8b2ecaf22bff99552ff3428791a31edbb","tid":1250211,"uid":260806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T03:55:55.000Z","msg":"香口膠雖然能夠過足牙癮<br />\n但清理香口膠留低嘅污跡就絕對唔過癮<br />\n喺偉大祖國隨處可見公共建築物上面殘留香口膠嘅痕跡<br />\n香港要成爲<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「一國」</span></strong>點解唔<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">共享榮耀</span></strong>呢<br />\n<br />\n如果「中出」都可以係協會<br />\n咁<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一人一口交</span></strong>都不過係楊修都估到嘅字謎<br />\n以大家嘅智慧<br />\n應該冇難度"},{"pid":"96425d5920f04208460ca547a51c5d47e867f6e1","tid":1250211,"uid":242834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e88330fdd0aa5adbc06a30af1ea2e1c172b922","tid":1250211,"uid":88435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310dbb7b8664994a59ca3f669b4887093677394a","tid":1250211,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:11:14.000Z","msg":"刑毀剪呀清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dbbc57c15e38724fcf3afd418314d2241acb51a","tid":1250211,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"310dbb7b8664994a59ca3f669b4887093677394a","tid":1250211,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:11:14.000Z","msg":"刑毀剪呀清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T04:11:27.000Z","msg":"打多左剪字，自膠"},{"pid":"44be8f076ef075c3556f68a5e8f1046aa